| **Type 2** | `{{ conflict.source2Type }}` |

**Decision needed**:
{% if conflict.conflictType == "deprecated_conflict" %}
- Determine if the deprecated source has a replacement that covers the same use cases
- If no replacement exists, keep the non-deprecated mapping
- If replacement exists, migrate to the replacement and update all consumers
{% elif conflict.conflictType == "cardinality" %}
- Determine the correct cardinality from domain requirements
- 1..1 (required, single) vs 0..* (optional, multiple) affects database schema and API contracts
- Consider backward compatibility with existing consumers
{% else %}
- Compare source ontologies for authority and recency
- Check if downstream consumers depend on either type
- Document the decision rationale in the ontology
{% endif %}

Record resolution: `ggen conflict resolve --entity "{{ conflict.entity | replace(from="https://ggen.dev/examples/conflict#", to="") }}" --property "{{ conflict.property | replace(from="https://ggen.dev/examples/conflict#", to="") }}" --strategy <strategy> --note "<rationale>"`

{% endfor %}
{% else %}
No manual interventions required. All conflicts are auto-resolvable.
